org.cef.browser.CefBrowser, org.cef.callback.CefNative, org.cef.handler.CefRenderHandler
public class MCEFBrowser extends org.cef.browser.CefBrowserOsr
An instance of an "Off-screen rendered" Chromium web browser. Complete with a renderer, keyboard and mouse inputs, optional browser control shortcuts, cursor handling, drag 入力が無効です: '&' drop support.
